These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
Pet: turtle, hedgehog
Beverage: 7up, tea
1. Pet:turtle is on the left of Beverage:7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Pet   | turtle  | hedgehog |
| Beverage     | tea | 7up  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
Transport: ship, car
Beverage: tea, cola
1. Transport:car is on the right of Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Transport    | ship      | car         |
| Beverage   | tea | cola |

 #################################
 
